#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn4.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.19:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. Rule "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Kassakasutta "
msgstr "19. A Farmer "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn4.19:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.19:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā bhikkhūnaṃ nibbānapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti. "
msgstr "Now at that time the Buddha was educating, encouraging, firing up, and inspiring the mendicants with a Dhamma talk about extinguishment. "

msgctxt "sn4.19:1.3"
msgid "Te ca bhikkhū aṭṭhiṃ katvā manasi katvā sabbacetasā samannāharitvā ohitasotā dhammaṃ suṇanti. "
msgstr "And those mendicants were paying heed, paying attention, engaging wholeheartedly, and lending an ear. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.115, pts2ed1.255, sc2
msgctxt "sn4.19:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho mārassa pāpimato etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Māra thought, "

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.2"
msgid "“ayaṃ kho samaṇo gotamo bhikkhūnaṃ nibbānapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya … pe … "
msgstr "“The ascetic Gotama is giving a Dhamma talk about extinguishment … and the mendicants are listening well. "

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.3"
msgid "yannūnāhaṃ yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkameyyaṃ vicakkhukammāyā”ti. "
msgstr "Why don’t I go and pull the wool over their eyes?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
# NOTE: BB has a typo here.
msgctxt "sn4.19:2.4"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā kassakavaṇṇaṃ abhinimminitvā mahantaṃ naṅgalaṃ khandhe karitvā dīghapācanayaṭṭhiṃ gahetvā haṭahaṭakeso sāṇasāṭinivattho kaddamamakkhitehi pādehi yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked manifested in the form of a farmer carrying a large plough on his shoulder. He held a long goad, his hair was messy, he was clad in sunn hemp, and his feet were muddy. He went up to the Buddha and said to him, "

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.5"
msgid "“api, samaṇa, balībadde addasā”ti? "
msgstr "“So, ascetic, did you happen to see any oxen?” "

# NOTE: A genuinely interesting question. Mara and oxen: what’s up with that?
#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.19:2.6"
msgid "“Kiṃ pana, pāpima, te balībaddehī”ti? "
msgstr "“But what have you to do with oxen, Wicked One?” "

# NOTE: Despite BB’s note, I think it’s unlikely that Mara was familiar with 5th century abhidhamma. If the phrase here means anything, it’s more likely to represent Mara’s clumsiness and confusion.
#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.19:2.7"
msgid "“Mameva, samaṇa, cakkhu, mama rūpā, mama cakkhusamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mine alone, ascetic, is the eye, mine are sights, mine is the field of eye contact consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.8"
msgid "Kuhiṃ me, samaṇa, gantvā mokkhasi? "
msgstr "Where can you escape me, ascetic? "

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.9"
msgid "Mameva, samaṇa, sotaṃ, mama saddā … pe … "
msgstr "Mine alone is the ear … "

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.10"
msgid "mameva, samaṇa, ghānaṃ, mama gandhā; "
msgstr "nose … "

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.11"
msgid "mameva, samaṇa, jivhā, mama rasā; "
msgstr "tongue … "

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.12"
msgid "mameva, samaṇa, kāyo, mama phoṭṭhabbā; "
msgstr "body … "

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.13"
msgid "mameva, samaṇa, mano, mama dhammā, mama manosamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ. "
msgstr "mind, mine are thoughts, mine is the field of mind contact consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn4.19:2.14"
msgid "Kuhiṃ me, samaṇa, gantvā mokkhasī”ti? "
msgstr "Where can you escape me, ascetic?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.116, pts2ed1.256, sc3
msgctxt "sn4.19:3.1"
msgid "“Taveva, pāpima, cakkhu, tava rūpā, tava cakkhusamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ. "
msgstr "“Yours alone, ascetic, is the eye, yours are sights, yours is the field of eye contact consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.2"
msgid "Yattha ca kho, pāpima, natthi cakkhu, natthi rūpā, natthi cakkhusamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ, agati tava tattha, pāpima. "
msgstr "Where there is no eye, no sights, no eye contact consciousness—you have no place there, Wicked One! "

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.3"
msgid "Taveva, pāpima, sotaṃ, tava saddā, tava sotasamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ. "
msgstr "Yours alone is the ear … "

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.4"
msgid "Yattha ca kho, pāpima, natthi sotaṃ, natthi saddā, natthi sotasamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ, agati tava tattha, pāpima. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.5"
msgid "Taveva, pāpima, ghānaṃ, tava gandhā, tava ghānasamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ. "
msgstr "nose … "

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.6"
msgid "Yattha ca kho, pāpima, natthi ghānaṃ, natthi gandhā, natthi ghānasamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ, agati tava tattha, pāpima. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.7"
msgid "Taveva, pāpima, jivhā, tava rasā, tava jivhāsamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "tongue … "

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.8"
msgid "taveva, pāpima, kāyo, tava phoṭṭhabbā, tava kāyasamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "body … "

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.9"
msgid "taveva, pāpima, mano, tava dhammā, tava manosamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ. "
msgstr "mind, yours are thoughts, yours is the field of mind contact consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn4.19:3.10"
msgid "Yattha ca kho, pāpima, natthi mano, natthi dhammā, natthi manosamphassaviññāṇāyatanaṃ, agati tava tattha, pāpimā”ti. "
msgstr "Where there is no mind, no thoughts, no mind contact consciousness—you have no place there, Wicked One!” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn4.19:4.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ vadanti mama yidanti, "
msgstr "“The things they call ‘mine’, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:4.2"
msgid "ye vadanti mamanti ca; "
msgstr "and those who say ‘it’s mine’: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:4.3"
msgid "Ettha ce te mano atthi, "
msgstr "if your mind remains there, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:4.4"
msgid "na me samaṇa mokkhasī”ti. "
msgstr "you won’t escape me, ascetic!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn4.19:5.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ vadanti na taṃ mayhaṃ, "
msgstr "“The things they speak of aren’t mine; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:5.2"
msgid "ye vadanti na te ahaṃ; "
msgstr "I’m not someone who speaks like that. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:5.3"
msgid "Evaṃ pāpima jānāhi, "
msgstr "So know this, Wicked One: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.19:5.4"
msgid "na me maggampi dakkhasī”ti. "
msgstr "you won’t even see the path I take.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn4.19:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā … pe … tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra … vanished right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
